1
00:00:09,360 --> 00:00:10,800
I've finished

2
00:00:11,079 --> 00:00:12,360
all overseas business.

3
00:00:12,600 --> 00:00:14,519
But the money left by my brother

4
00:00:14,760 --> 00:00:16,280
overseas

5
00:00:16,800 --> 00:00:19,720
can only be used by the company

6
00:00:19,839 --> 00:00:20,879
after a new heir

7
00:00:21,080 --> 00:00:22,479
is selected.

8
00:00:23,960 --> 00:00:25,519
I'm back

9
00:00:26,159 --> 00:00:28,120
to urge the board of directors

10
00:00:28,679 --> 00:00:31,239
to select a new chairman as soon as possible.

11
00:00:32,479 --> 00:00:33,640
Let my brother

12
00:00:34,159 --> 00:00:35,159
be the chairman.

13
00:00:35,919 --> 00:00:37,040
The position is originally his.

14
00:00:39,879 --> 00:00:40,479
Chengjing,

15
00:00:40,959 --> 00:00:42,640
your mother has a lot of shares

16
00:00:42,640 --> 00:00:43,839
in the group.

17
00:00:44,360 --> 00:00:46,839
She probably won't agree with your decision.

18
00:01:04,679 --> 00:01:05,399
Uncle,

19
00:01:06,560 --> 00:01:07,920
I'll talk to her

20
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:09,119
when she comes back.

21
00:01:33,599 --> 00:01:34,239
Who is it?

22
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:41,920
Mr. Gu.

23
00:01:42,560 --> 00:01:43,440
I need you

24
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:46,360
to do me a favor.

25
00:01:48,080 --> 00:01:50,039
I haven't changed the sheets and duvet covers for half a month.

26
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:51,319
Could you go and change them for me?

27
00:01:52,119 --> 00:01:52,759
Okay.

28
00:01:53,039 --> 00:01:53,679
Let's go.

29
00:02:31,320 --> 00:02:32,959
Mr. Gu, I've finished.

30
00:02:48,719 --> 00:02:51,040
Young Master Yan, you're still up this late?

31
00:02:52,559 --> 00:02:53,279
What were you doing?

32
00:02:54,200 --> 00:02:56,040
I just went to

33
00:02:58,399 --> 00:02:59,760
change the sheets for Mr. Gu.

34
00:03:08,279 --> 00:03:09,719
Young Master Yan,

35
00:03:09,839 --> 00:03:11,040
do you need anything?

36
00:03:15,519 --> 00:03:18,119
Do you also need to change the sheets?

37
00:03:19,239 --> 00:03:19,880
Close the door.

38
00:03:26,760 --> 00:03:28,040
Then go to bed early.

39
00:03:53,119 --> 00:03:54,439
As for the heir,

40
00:03:54,959 --> 00:03:56,200
I don't have any opinion.

41
00:03:57,119 --> 00:03:59,640
Chengyan is doing well in the company.

42
00:04:00,040 --> 00:04:02,439
The acquisition of Su's Art Gallery

43
00:04:03,160 --> 00:04:04,399
was very well done.

44
00:04:05,200 --> 00:04:05,880
And Chengjing,

45
00:04:06,719 --> 00:04:07,999
although you are new to the company,

46
00:04:08,200 --> 00:04:10,279
you are young and promising,

47
00:04:10,920 --> 00:04:11,999
with a bright future.

48
00:04:13,640 --> 00:04:14,520
We are all family.

49
00:04:15,160 --> 00:04:18,480
No matter who takes over the company,

50
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:21,639
you must continue to run

51
00:04:22,160 --> 00:04:23,160
the business left by your father.

52
00:04:23,600 --> 00:04:24,999
That's the most important thing.

53
00:04:27,800 --> 00:04:28,600
All right.

54
00:04:29,759 --> 00:04:30,439
Let's eat.

55
00:04:43,239 --> 00:04:43,920
Xiaoxue.

56
00:04:44,759 --> 00:04:46,199
Pour me a glass of red wine too.

57
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:48,360
Okay.

58
00:04:50,319 --> 00:04:50,960
Uncle.

59
00:04:51,639 --> 00:04:53,199
I'm not feeling well today.

60
00:04:53,960 --> 00:04:55,679
Xiaoxue needs to take care of me.

61
00:04:56,319 --> 00:04:57,079
Excuse me.

62
00:05:04,679 --> 00:05:05,600
Uncle.

63
00:05:06,639 --> 00:05:08,559
Xiaoxue is the personal care I found for Chengyan.

64
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:11,040
If you don't want the servant to do it,

65
00:05:11,520 --> 00:05:12,559
I can find one for you.

66
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:14,600
No need.

67
00:05:24,559 --> 00:05:25,439
Young Master Yan,

68
00:05:25,639 --> 00:05:27,679
you don't have to be mad at them.

69
00:05:28,079 --> 00:05:29,960
Mr. Gu asked me to do it,

70
00:05:30,199 --> 00:05:31,840
so it's my duty.

71
00:05:32,920 --> 00:05:34,600
You're my personal care.

72
00:05:35,160 --> 00:05:36,239
How can you take care of others?

73
00:05:41,639 --> 00:05:42,319
Xiaoxue,

74
00:05:43,520 --> 00:05:44,280
stop massaging.

75
00:05:44,280 --> 00:05:45,079
I have a question for you.

76
00:05:47,439 --> 00:05:48,679
What's that?

77
00:05:50,079 --> 00:05:51,679
It's a birthmark.

78
00:05:52,119 --> 00:05:53,759
Because it looks like a snowflake,

79
00:05:53,759 --> 00:05:55,600
my mom named me Xiaoxue.

80
00:05:58,079 --> 00:05:59,800
What about your mom?

81
00:06:00,840 --> 00:06:03,040
My mom died long ago.

82
00:06:03,239 --> 00:06:05,160
I grew up in an orphanage.

83
00:06:08,679 --> 00:06:09,559
Sorry.

84
00:06:10,360 --> 00:06:11,480
Pour me another glass of wine.

85
00:06:14,559 --> 00:06:15,400
It's empty, Young Master Yan.

86
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:16,920
Should I get you another bottle?

87
00:06:17,999 --> 00:06:18,559
No need.

88
00:06:19,199 --> 00:06:21,239
I'll go pick one from the cellar later.

89
00:06:22,759 --> 00:06:23,360
Okay.

90
00:06:35,160 --> 00:06:36,319
Look into

91
00:06:36,879 --> 00:06:38,520
Ji Xiaoxue's background.

92
00:06:39,639 --> 00:06:41,040
I need all the information.

93
00:06:42,199 --> 00:06:42,920
Make it quick.

94
00:06:50,360 --> 00:06:51,720
Do you always come here?

95
00:06:52,759 --> 00:06:54,480
I've been running around

96
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:55,280
for the Su Group acquisition,

97
00:06:55,639 --> 00:06:58,199
I've been visiting art galleries across the country,

98
00:06:58,759 --> 00:07:01,119
looking for a way to deal with it.

99
00:07:01,759 --> 00:07:02,480
Of course,

100
00:07:02,920 --> 00:07:04,600
I also really enjoy art.

101
00:07:06,280 --> 00:07:07,840
I often came here after returning.

102
00:07:08,759 --> 00:07:10,239
But I think there are issues with these galleries.

103
00:07:10,960 --> 00:07:12,239
Not only are the exhibits incomplete,

104
00:07:12,920 --> 00:07:13,999
but the design is also problematic.

105
00:07:14,239 --> 00:07:14,960
Look,

106
00:07:15,439 --> 00:07:16,280
this gravel path.

107
00:07:16,400 --> 00:07:17,879
Some ladies are wearing high heels.

108
00:07:17,879 --> 00:07:18,720
Isn't that just...

109
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:29,639
Are you okay?

110
00:07:30,999 --> 00:07:31,720
I'm fine.

111
00:07:32,239 --> 00:07:32,840
It doesn't hurt.

112
00:07:50,960 --> 00:07:51,879
It's okay, let me.

113
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:00,720
When drinking red wine,

114
00:08:00,960 --> 00:08:01,920
you should first smell it,

115
00:08:04,239 --> 00:08:05,319
to smell its fruity aroma,

116
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:06,920
and then taste it,

117
00:08:07,480 --> 00:08:08,439
to taste its lingering sweetness.

118
00:08:09,400 --> 00:08:10,040
Have a try.

119
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:21,439
How is it?

120
00:08:23,199 --> 00:08:23,999
I'm a bit dizzy.

121
00:08:30,880 --> 00:08:33,240
This time, just smell it, don't drink it.

122
00:08:38,479 --> 00:08:39,160
How is it?

123
00:08:40,920 --> 00:08:42,839
This is the taste of wine?

124
00:08:45,479 --> 00:08:46,599
You're not smelling it right.

125
00:08:54,040 --> 00:08:55,719
It has a strong fruity aroma.

126
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:57,959
Let me smell it again.

127
00:09:23,839 --> 00:09:24,640
Chengjing,

128
00:09:25,160 --> 00:09:26,640
you haven't tried this wine yet.

129
00:09:26,760 --> 00:09:27,880
I bring it here for you.

130
00:09:27,880 --> 00:09:28,439
Okay.

131
00:09:32,599 --> 00:09:33,400
Why is it gone?

132
00:09:36,079 --> 00:09:37,479
Did your brother take it away?

133
00:09:38,800 --> 00:09:40,280
Why don't you call Chengyan?

134
00:09:43,439 --> 00:09:45,400
Young Master Yan, he's calling you.

135
00:09:45,400 --> 00:09:46,120
What should I do?

136
00:09:50,439 --> 00:09:51,559
I don't have my phone.

137
00:10:03,479 --> 00:10:04,280
He didn't answer.

138
00:10:06,000 --> 00:10:06,439
Okay.

139
00:10:06,839 --> 00:10:08,559
Let's see if there's any inside.

140
00:10:08,760 --> 00:10:09,319
Okay.

141
00:10:22,120 --> 00:10:22,839
Chengjing,

142
00:10:24,839 --> 00:10:26,160
this bottle of liquor is also very good.

143
00:10:26,160 --> 00:10:26,839
Take a look.

144
00:10:27,479 --> 00:10:28,439
Let's drink this one.

145
00:10:28,439 --> 00:10:29,079
That's fine.

146
00:10:29,760 --> 00:10:30,359
Let's go.

147
00:10:30,359 --> 00:10:30,959
Go.
